dct_title_s: Gaza Strip, December 1991 (Israeli occupied - status to be determined)
dct_description_sm: [United States. Central Intelligence Agency]. North Decimal Degree 31.600000. South Decimal Degree 31.2167. East Decimal Degree 34.5833. West Decimal Degree 34.2167. Universal transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by spot heights. Map shows: "built-up area", Israeli-developed area (civilian) beyond the 1950 Armistice Line, "Israeli-development area (military) beyond the 1950 Armistice Line; Israel-developed refugee housing area; UNRWA Palestinian refugee camp. Map no.: 802022 (00036) 3-92.
